  "Apply": "应用",
  "The instruction sent to the model. Defines how the tracker generates data.": "发送给模型的指令。定义追踪器如何生成数据。",
  "The JSON schema defining the output structure. Must be valid JSON.": "定义输出结构的JSON模式。必须是有效JSON。",
  "Removes all tracker snapshots from this chat. Settings preserved.": "删除所有追踪器快照。设置保留。",
  "Resets injection method, profiles, lorebook mode, etc. to defaults. Tracker data preserved.": "重置注入方法等为默认值。追踪器数据保留。",
  "ScenePulse internal debug log (normalizer, extraction, generation).": "ScenePulse内部调试日志（规范化、提取、生成）。",
  "Full browser console output including SillyTavern and other extensions.": "包含SillyTavern和扩展的完整控制台输出。",
  "Raw tracker JSON from the most recent generation.": "最近生成的原始追踪器JSON。",
  "In Separate mode, this is the full API response. In Together mode, this is the extracted JSON block that was stripped from the AI's narrative response.": "分离模式为完整API响应。合并模式为提取的JSON。",
  "The AI writes its normal response, then appends tracker JSON at the end. ScenePulse automatically extracts and hides the JSON.": "AI撰写响应后附加追踪器JSON。ScenePulse自动提取并隐藏。",
  "If the AI omits the tracker payload, ScenePulse can automatically run a separate API call to recover. Requires a connection profile to be configured.": "如AI遗漏数据，ScenePulse可自动单独API调用恢复。需配置连接。",
  "Dramatic": "戏剧性",
  "Intense": "激烈",
  "Comedic": "喜剧",
  "Twist": "转折",
  "Exploratory": "探索性",
  "None suggested yet": "暂无建议",
  "After the AI responds, a separate quiet API call generates the tracker JSON independently. Expect ~250–300s total per message (narrative + wait + tracker).": "AI响应后，静默API独立生成追踪器JSON。每条消息~250–300秒。",
  "✓ Single API call — typically ~100–120s total": "✓ 单次API — ~100–120秒",
  "✓ No profile switching — eliminates message deletion risk": "✓ 无需切换配置 — 无删除风险",
  "✓ AI has full narrative context for accurate tracking": "✓ AI拥有完整上下文",
  "✓ 2–3× faster than Separate mode in practice": "✓ 比分离模式快2–3倍",
  "✗ Uses tokens from the main response budget (~1,700 tokens for tracker)": "✗ 使用主响应令牌（~1,700）",
  "✗ May slightly reduce narrative length on token-limited models": "✗ 可能略微减少叙述长度",
  "✓ Clean responses — narrative never token-competes with tracker": "✓ 干净响应 — 不争夺令牌",
  "✓ Dedicated token budget for tracker output": "✓ 追踪器专用令牌预算",
  "✓ Can use a different connection profile/preset": "✓ 可以使用不同的配置/预设",
  "✗ Two API calls per message — 2–3× slower than Together mode": "✗ 每条消息两次API — 慢2–3倍",
  "✗ ~12s dead time between calls (chat save + preset switching)": "✗ 调用间~12秒空闲",
  "✗ Tracker prompt is ~10K+ tokens at 8 context msgs — reduce to 3–4 for speed": "✗ 8条消息时~10K+ — 减少到3–4",
  "✗ Profile switching can cause message deletion (race condition with other extensions)": "✗ 配置切换可能导致消息删除",
  "✗ Embeds previous snapshot into narrative call (~1.9K tokens) unless Embed snapshots = 0": "✗ 嵌入快照≠0时含上一快照（~1.9K）",
  "How many recent messages to include when generating tracker updates.": "生成追踪器更新时包含多少条最近消息。",
  "Separate mode only — Together mode uses ST's full context automatically.": "仅限分离模式 — 合并模式自动使用ST上下文。",
  "Fastest. Good for simple 1-on-1 scenes (~5K token prompt)": "最快。适合一对一场景（~5K）",
  "Balanced. Recommended for most scenes (~8–12K tokens)": "均衡。推荐大多数场景（~8–12K）",
  "Better continuity for complex multi-character scenes (~12–20K tokens)": "复杂多角色场景连续性（~12–20K）",
  "Maximum context but significantly slower and more expensive": "最大上下文但更慢且更贵",
  "This is the biggest factor in Separate mode speed. At 8 msgs your tracker prompt is ~10K tokens — doubling roughly doubles generation time. Lower values (3–4) can cut tracker time by 40–60%.": "分离模式速度最大因素。8条消息~10K — 翻倍时间翻倍。3–4减少40–60%。",
  "Separate mode only.": "仅限分离模式。",
  "How many times to retry if the tracker API call returns invalid JSON.": "无效JSON时重试次数。",
  "Built-in preset: temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096. Optimized for structured JSON output on GLM-5.": "内置预设：temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096。GLM-5 JSON优化。",
  "Embed recent scene snapshots into the narrative conversation context so the AI can reference tracker state while writing. Only applies in Separate mode. The tracker's own API call always receives the previous snapshot regardless of this setting.": "将场景快照嵌入叙述上下文。仅分离模式。追踪器始终接收上一快照。",
  "Each embedded snapshot adds ~1.9K tokens to your narrative prompt. Set to 0 to eliminate this overhead — the tracker API call still receives previous state independently. Set to 1 for narrative continuity (AI remembers scene details). Values above 1 are rarely beneficial.": "每个快照+~1.9K。0消除开销。1保持连续性。1以上很少有益。",
  "Injected as invisible context — AI treats it as authoritative background info. Best for continuity without polluting the conversation.": "作为不可见上下文注入。AI视为权威背景信息。",
  "Appears as if the user said it — some models respond more attentively.": "显示为用户发言 — 某些模型更专注地响应。",
  "Appears as previous AI output — can reinforce the AI's own memory but may confuse some models.": "显示为AI之前的输出 — 增强记忆但可能混淆。",
  "Separate generation runs an isolated API call — it needs lorebook context injected since ST won't provide it automatically.": "分离生成运行独立API — 需注入知识库上下文。",
  "Together mode uses the normal generation — ST already injects lorebooks into context, so including them here would be redundant.": "合并模式使用正常生成 — ST已注入知识库，此处多余。",
